quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  78,31,Ndithudi kwa anthu oopa Mulungu kudzakhala kupambana
  78,32,Minda ndi m’minda ya mphesa
  78,33,Ndi a namwali akulu akulu ofanana zaka
  78,34,Ndi chikho chodzadza
  78,35,Kumeneko iwo sadzamva mawu opanda pake kapena nkhani zabodza
  78,36,Imeneyi ndiyo mphotho yochokera kwa Ambuye wako ndipo ndi mphotho yokwanira
  78,37,"Ambuye wa Kumwamba ndi dziko lapansi ndi zonse zimene zili pakati pawo, Mwini chisoni chosatha ndipo iwo sadzatha kulankhula naye"
  78,38,Patsiku limene Mzimu ndi angelo adzaima pa mizere ndipo palibe amene adzalankhula kupatula yekhayo amene adzalandira chilolezo cha Mwini chifundo chosatha ndipo adzanena chinthu chimene chili choona
  78,39,"Ndithudi tsiku limeneli ndi loona, motero iye amene afuna, mulekeni atsatire njira yobwerera kwa Ambuye wake"
  78,40,"Ndithudi takuchenjezani za chilango chowawa chimene chili nkudza posachedwa. Tsiku limene munthu adzayang’ana ntchito zimene manja ake adatsogoza, ndipo osakhulupirira adzati: “Kalanga ine, ndikanakhala dothi.”"